# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### PDFSHIFT_API_KEY
Your PDFShift API key for PDF generation.

**How to get it:**
1. Sign up at https://pdfshift.io
2. Get your API key from the dashboard
3. Add to Vercel environment variables

**Free tier:** 50 PDFs per month

